dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Kenneth Howard. May I have your name, please?
Hi Kenneth, my name is Lauren Campbell.
Nice to meet you, Lauren. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six eight two one and my date of birth is zero three zero five one nine eight seven.
Thank you, Lauren. One more question, could you confirm the make and model of your vehicle for our records?
Of course, I drive a two zero one four Toyota Camry.
Thank you for providing that information, Lauren. It looks like everything is in order. Do you have any other questions or concerns for me today?
No, I think that covers everything for now. Thank you, Kenneth.
You're welcome, Lauren. Thank you for reaching out to us. If you need any assistance in the future, feel free to contact us. Have a great day!
